sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Sensor as ESP32 Hardware
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant AI as Isolation Forest
    participant DB as SQLite DB
    actor Admin as Next.js Dashboard

    Sensor->>+API: HTTP POST /detect-anomaly {ldr: 450}
    API->>+AI: model.predict([450])
    AI-->>-API: Score: 0.15, Normal
    API->>DB: INSERT (Normal)
    API-->>-Sensor: HTTP 200 OK

    Note over Sensor,API: 2 Seconds Later

    Sensor->>+API: HTTP POST /detect-anomaly {ldr: 980}
    API->>+AI: model.predict([980])
    AI-->>-API: Score: 0.95, Anomaly
    API->>DB: INSERT (Alert: SPIKE)
    API-->>-Sensor: HTTP 200 OK

    loop Every 3 Seconds
        Admin->>+API: HTTP GET /dashboard/stats
        API-->>-Admin: Return JSON Array
        Admin->>Admin: React Component Hydration
    end
